title: Ancylosis plumbatella
text: Ancylosis plumbatella is a species of <a href="Pyralidae">snout moth</a> in the genus "<a href="Ancylosis">Ancylosis</a>". It was described by <a href="%C3%89mile%20Louis%20Ragonot">Ragonot</a>, in 1888. It is found in the Achal Tekke region in central <a href="Asia">Asia</a>.
